trans-unit.source: Configures an HTTP module for a Web application.
trans-unit.target: Konfigurerer en HTTP-modul for et webprogram.

trans-unit.source: The HttpModulesSection class provides a way to programmatically access and modify the `httpModules` section of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Klassen HttpModulesSection gjør det mulig å programmatisk tilgang til og endre den `httpModules` delen av konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: This type is part of a group that includes the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleAction> and the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleActionCollection> types.
trans-unit.target: Denne typen er en del av en gruppe som inneholder den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleAction>og <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleActionCollection>typer.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleActionCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleAction>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The HttpModulesSection can read and write information from and to the related section of the configuration file according to the section property <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A> whose value is <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For HttpModulesSection kan lese og skrive informasjon fra og relaterte delen av konfigurasjonsfilen i henhold til den delen egenskapen <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A>der verdien er <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition>.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition> </xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModulesSection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModulesSection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The HttpModulesSection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren HttpModulesSection skal ikke brukes direkte fra koden.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
You obtain an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpModulesSection> class by using the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du hente en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpModulesSection>klassen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpModulesSection>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleActionCollection"></xref> of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleAction"></xref> modules contained by the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModulesSection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleActionCollection"> </xref> av <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleAction"> </xref> moduler som inneholder den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModulesSection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The collection returned by this method does not refer to any actual element in the underlying configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen ble returnert av denne metoden refererer ikke til noen faktiske element i underliggende konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.source: It is an ASP.NET infrastructure construct that allows easy access to the modules it contains.
trans-unit.target: Det er en konstruksjon for ASP.NET-infrastruktur som gir enkel tilgang til moduler den inneholder.

trans-unit.source: This is a common pattern for handling the elements of a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en vanlig mønster for håndtering av elementene i en konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleActionCollection"></xref> that contains the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleAction"></xref> objects, or modules, defined by the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModulesSection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleActionCollection"> </xref> som inneholder den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModuleAction"> </xref> objekter eller moduler som er definert av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.HttpModulesSection"> </xref>.
